    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### ACCESS360 \u2014 Live Fleet Health  \u00b7  Grafana Live via MQTT\nStreaming straight from **HiveMQ** (`iot-hivemq:1883`) \u2014 no database. Gateway `43250372`. **Velocity (IPS)** comes from `\u2026/derived/vib` (flattened from the on-demand full `dyn/vib/notify` by the Node-RED velocity normalizer), so IPS panels fill when a full reading is taken. Health panels stream continuously as sensors report."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Vibration velocity \u2014 IPS (in/s)",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
